==名人==
绩溪县以[[胡姓|胡姓]]居多，而绩溪有五个族属不同的胡氏家族，其中四个皆有名人，前中共中央总书记[[胡锦涛|胡锦涛]]属于龙川胡，胡雪岩和胡适属明经胡。<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 《人物》杂志 | title = 绩溪：溪水萦流 人文深厚 | url = http://www.renwu.com.cn/UserFiles/magazine/article/RW0195_200507010958006383.asp | author = 潘小平 | date = 2005年第5期 | accessdate = 2010-12-05 | archive-date = 2010-12-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101211163033/http://www.renwu.com.cn/UserFiles/magazine/article/RW0195_200507010958006383.asp | dead-url = yes }}</ref>而明经胡为李姓后裔，故又称“李改胡”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ah.anhuinews.com/system/2003/01/20/000224556.shtml|title=文摘周刊：胡锦涛与安徽绩溪|publisher=中安在线|date=2003-01-20|accessdate=2015-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304083432/http://ah.anhuinews.com/system/2003/01/20/000224556.shtml|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
* [[胡雪岩|胡雪岩]]
* [[汪華|汪華]]
* [[胡仔|胡仔]]
* [[胡天注|胡天注]]
* [[胡開文|胡開文]]
